Package: stylex
Type: Package
Title: Package for updating styles in docx file for making template
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author: niszet [aut, cph, cre]
Maintainer: niszet <niszet_dev@gmail.com>
Description: Support to modify the style settings in docx file.
    This package expects Pandoc's docx template file but any other docx can be applied.
    This package will NOT check the value which given. See the reference of OOXML and MS Word's behavior.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
Imports:
  dplyr,
  fs,
  janitor,
  officer,
  stringr,
  xml2
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 2.3.2)
